# Documentation Language

## Rules

- Governance and repo-maintenance documents are English-first.
- Archived rationale records may remain in their original language.
- Do not rewrite or delete user-authored discussion records unless the user explicitly asks for it.
- Preserve untracked template or working material when ownership is unclear; ask before deleting it.
